('FAQ_answer-6', 'International orders will be dealt with on a case by case basis as shipping costs vary between different weights, dimensions and countries. If you live outside the UK and are interested in something, please let contact <font color=''red''>info@sundaydogshop.com</font>'),
('policy_privacy', 'Sunday Dog respects your right to privacy. We are committed to protecting and maintaining our customers'' privacy and making the use of our website as simple and secure as possible.<br><br>We collect personal information about you, such as a name, address, telephone number, email address, credit card number, or information about activities which can be directly linked to you, to process your order and deliver your purchases. Where (and only where) consented to by you, we may contact you occasionally by email with promotional information and news, from which you can unsubscribe at any time.<br><br>All the data collected is securely stored using industry standard firewalls and can only be accessed by Sunday Dog. The secure server software encrypts all personally identifiable information you input when you place an order before it is sent to us.<br><br>Electronic payment transactions are handled by WorldPay using Secure Socket Layers (SSL) which ensure that data is encrypted and thus protected.  We do not store or have access to your card details at any point in a transaction. If we suspect suspicious use of your card we will contact you by telephone or email.<br><br>We use cookies which are certain types of text information we receive and store when you interact with our websites, emails, and online advertising. Our purpose is to allow the websites to work correctly, to evaluate use of the website, to support website analytics and marketing campaigns and to allow a user to store items in their shopping basket. For more information on cookies and how to disable them, you can consult the information provided by the Interactive Advertising Bureau at www.allaboutcookies.org.<br><br>We may share information about you with service providers or suppliers that help with our business operations. Examples are shipping vendors, billing and refund vendors, and credit card processors. We require these service providers and suppliers to keep the information secure. We also prohibit them from using your information for any purposes other than those requested by us.<br><br>Please check our privacy policy periodically for changes. We will also notify you of significant updates and will post the date it was last updated at the bottom of the privacy policy.'),
('policy_consent', 'Sunday Dog respects your right to privacy. We are committed to protecting and maintaining our customers'' privacy and making the use of our website as simple and secure as possible.<br><br>We collect personal information about you, such as a name, address, telephone number, email address, credit card number, or information about activities which can be directly linked to you, to process your order and deliver your purchases. Where (and only where) consented to by you, we may contact you occasionally by email with promotional information and news, from which you can unsubscribe at any time.<br><br>All the data collected is securely stored using industry standard firewalls and can only be accessed by Sunday Dog. The secure server software encrypts all personally identifiable information you input when you place an order before it is sent to us.<br><br>Electronic payment transactions are handled by WorldPay using Secure Socket Layers (SSL) which ensure that data is encrypted and thus protected.  We do not sWhile Sunday Dog takes reasonable steps to safeguard and to prevent unauthorized access to your personal information, we cannot be responsible for the acts of those who gain unauthorized access, and we make no warranty, express, implied, or otherwise, that we will prevent unauthorized access to your private information. In no event shall Sunday Dog be liable for any damages (whether consequential, direct, incidental, indirect, punitive, special or otherwise) arising out of, or in any way connected with, a third party''s unauthorized access to your personal information, regardless of whether such damages are based on contract, strict liability, tort or other theories of liability, and also regardless of whether Sunday Dog was given actual or constructive notice that damages were possible.'),
('policy_return', 'We want to ensure your complete satisfaction with all of our products. In the event you must return or exchange a purchase please follow the directions below.<ul><li>The enquiry of a refund must be made inside a 14 day period after receiving the product and must be sent back inside a period of 30 days.</li><li>Merchandise must be unused and returned in its original packaging to be considered for a full refund or exchange.</li><li>We reserve the right to determine whether an item has been used or washed. Please note that original shipping charges are non-refundable and customers are responsible for all return shipping costs.</li><li>In the event an item was damaged during shipping or sent in error please call or email us  within 48 hours of receipt. In these cases Sunday Dog will pay the return shipping charges.</li><li>We do not take responsibility for goods damaged by the shipping company.</li><li>Refunds are not available for custom or personalized orders, discounted orders, or unless otherwise stated at the point of sale.</li></ul>'),
('policy_payment', 'Payment is due upon placement of order.<br><br>Payment by Credit Card<br><br>We accept Visa, and MasterCard<br><br>Payment via PayPal<br><br>We use Paypal because we believe it to be a very safe way to buy goods online. And it''s easy! You do not have to have a Paypal account or log-in to anything to process your order. Simply follow the instructions on the checkout page. Paypal is an international secure payment service used by millions of people every day for purchasing goods online.<br><br>Payment by Bank Transfer (within Thailand only)<br><br>Should you wish to do so, we are also able to accept payment via direct bank transfer, but goods will not be dispatched until funds are received.<br><br>Processing Your Order<br><br>We try to process all orders within 24hrs of receiving them, however there are occasions where this will vary. If your order is received by 2pm, we''ll do our best to dispatch it the next working day.'),
